        <div class="blog-header">
            <h1 class="blog-title">Automating Lead <span>Follow-Up:</span> From Cold Leads to Booked Calls</h1>
            <div class="blog-meta">
                <span>üìÖ July 12, 2024</span>
                <span>‚è∞ 5 min read</span>
                <span>üìä Sales Automation</span>
            </div>
